creator: Niktec
descriptionHtml:
compare Popular DNS servers by displaying the DNS query speed, so you can find out which DNS server is the fastest for your network or smartphone.

why should you change your DNS server? 🤔
• faster loading times of webpages 🚀
• Adblock (E.g AdGuard) 🚫
• privacy (E.g 1.1.1.1) 🔒
• unlock blocked content 🕵️

features:
• compare the query/reply speed of Popular DNS servers
• add custom servers to compare them
• Line chart to see the Repeatability of each DNS server
descriptionShort: Find the fastest DNS server for your phone or network

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
• fixed bugs
• added adfree option
• new settings page
• moved reload button to the top to show more content on small phones
